.TH XIL\-REGEN "1" "2026\-04\-05" "xil\-pipeline 0.1.3" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
xil\-regen
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B xil\-regen
[-h] --episode EPISODE [--parsed PARSED] [--cast CAST] [--show SHOW] [--output OUTPUT] [--speakers SPEAKERS]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Regenerate a production script markdown from parsed JSON.

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-episode\fR \fI\,EPISODE\/\fR
Episode tag (e.g. S02E03)

.TP
\fB\-\-parsed\fR \fI\,PARSED\/\fR
Override parsed JSON path

.TP
\fB\-\-cast\fR \fI\,CAST\/\fR
Override cast config path

.TP
\fB\-\-show\fR \fI\,SHOW\/\fR
Show name override (default: from project.json)

.TP
\fB\-\-output\fR \fI\,OUTPUT\/\fR
Output markdown path (default: scripts/revised_<slug>_{TAG}.md)

.TP
\fB\-\-speakers\fR \fI\,SPEAKERS\/\fR
Path to speakers.json (default: auto\-detect from CWD, then built\-in)

